3 pounds chicken
2 eggs
1 cup flour
2 tbsp Colonel's secret herbs and spices mix
2 cups cooking oil
*
heat oil to 375
cut up chicken
beat eggs until they scream for mercy
put flour, spice mix into bowl
dip chicken pieces into eggs
dredge chicken in flour and spice mix
fry chicken in oil until done (about 30 min.)
*
Serves 4
